public function GetFormattedTaggedValueString(tags) dim taggedValues as EA.Element.TaggedValues set taggedValues = tags
dim counter counter = taggedValues.count
dim swrid set swrid = taggedValues.getat(0)
dim i dim formattedString
for i = 1 to counter dim tag as EA.TaggedValue set tag = taggedValues.GetAt(i-1) ' TODO: Note가 있는 경우 노트를 value로 바꿔야 함. dim name, value
name = Replace(tag.Name, "/", "") name = Replace(name, " ", "")
if StrComp(tag.Value, "<memo>") = 0 then value = tag.Notes else value = tag.Value end if
' < > 문자를 escape 함 value = Replace(value, "<", "?")
formattedString = formattedString & "<" & name & ">" & value & "</" & name & ">" next
GetFormattedTaggedValueString = formattedString end function
public function GetEscapedXMLValueString(value) dim formattedString
formattedString = value
formattedString = Replace(formattedString, "<", "<") formattedString = Replace(formattedString, ">", ">") formattedString = Replace(formattedString, "&", "&") formattedString = Replace(formattedString, """", """)
GetEscapedXMLValueString = formattedString end function
public function DBGetFormattedTaggedValueString(table, where) dim i ' read db and insert tagged value item to returnValue dim tags, notes tags = DBGetFieldValueArrayString( "Value", table, where ) notes = DBGetFieldValueArrayString( "Notes", table, where )
dim tagIdx, nodeString for tagIdx = 0 to ubound(tags) ' tag value 가 <memo> 인경우는 Notes 필드를 읽어야 함. AND <memo> 는 XML 데이터를 EA가 읽어들일때 오류까지 발생. dim isMemo, memoString isMemo = StrComp(tags(tagIdx), "<memo>") if isMemo = 0 then tags(tagIdx) = notes(tagIdx) end if
nodeString = nodeString & "<TaggedValue_" & CStr(tagIdx) & ">" & tags(tagIdx) & "</TaggedValue_" & CStr(tagIdx) & ">" next
DBGetFormattedTaggedValueString = nodeString
end function
' t_object 테이블의 Notes 인경우에 한정 함. function DBGetNotesValueString( table, whereClause )
DBGetNotesValueString = ""
' Construct and execute the query dim sql dim queryResult sql = "SELECT Note AS [Notes] FROM " & table & " WHERE " & whereClause queryResult = Repository.SQLQuery( sql )
dim queryDOM set queryDOM = XMLParseXML( queryResult ) if not queryDOM is nothing then
DBGetNotesValueString = XMLGetNodeText( queryDOM, "/EADATA/Dataset_0/Data/Row/" & "Notes" & "[0]" )
end if
end function
sub DBSetElementTaggedValue( theElement, taggedValueName, taggedValueValue, replaceExisting )
if not theElement is nothing and Len(taggedValueName) > 0 then dim taggedValue as EA.TaggedValue set taggedValue = nothing
' If replaceExisting was specified then attempt to get a tagged value from the element ' with the provided name if not replaceExisting = false then set taggedValue = theElement.TaggedValues.GetByName( taggedValueName ) end if
if taggedValue is nothing then set taggedValue = theElement.TaggedValues.AddNew( taggedValueName, taggedValueValue ) else taggedValue.Value = taggedValueValue end if
taggedValue.Update() end if
end sub

public function MakeSwDsComponentInterface(objectID)
' Show the script output window Repository.EnsureOutputVisible "Script"
LOGinfo("Making Component Interface" & objectID)
dim ele as EA.Element
set ele = Repository.GetElementByID(objectID)
dim method as EA.Method dim methodCnt, interfaceCnt, unitCnt methodCnt = ele.Methods.Count
dim returnValue returnValue = ""
dim i interfaceCnt = 0 returnValue = "<EADATA><Dataset_0>"
for i = 0 to methodCnt - 1 set method = ele.Methods.GetAt(i) LOGDebug(method.Name & method.Visibility)
if method.Visibility = "Public" then interfaceCnt = interfaceCnt + 1
returnValue = returnValue & "<Data><Row>"
returnValue = returnValue & "<IfName>" & method.Name & "</IfName>"
returnValue = returnValue & GetFormattedTaggedValueString( method.TaggedValues )
dim proto, y dim param as EA.Parameter proto = method.ReturnType & " " & method.Name & " (" for y = 0 to method.Parameters.Count - 1 if y > 0 then proto = proto & ", " End if set param = method.Parameters.GetAt(y)
proto = proto & param.Type & " " & param.Name Next proto = proto & ")"
returnValue = returnValue & "<Proto>" & proto & "</Proto>" returnValue = returnValue & "<Notes>" & method.Notes & "</Notes>"
returnValue = returnValue & "</Row></Data>" End if Next
returnValue = returnValue & "</Dataset_0></EADATA>"
unitCnt = methodCnt - interfaceCnt
MakeSwDsComponentInterface = returnValue
end function
